    <skos:definition>return DGGS-JSON-FG representation; using dggsPlace to encode geometry points quantized to sub-zone; represented as local indices from 1 to the number of sub-zones corresponding to the DGGRS deterministic sub-zone order; with a special value of 0 representing an artificial node</skos:definition>
